title: Only An Excuse 2013 - BBC Scotland Football Comedy
description:
Only an Excuse?

Jonathan Watson leads the team as football's premier comedy sketch show returns with its traditional helping of Hogmanay satire, mercilessly lampooning the sporting heroes and villains of the past 12 months, offering pearls of wisdom on the state of the game and looking back at the events that made the headlines on and off the pitch

Category Football Comedy
